=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.instInhabited\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabited</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.instInhabited","kind":"instance","line":82,"name":"Computation.instInhabited","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L82-L83"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.empty\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">empty</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`empty α` is the computation that never returns, an infinite sequence of\n`think`s. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.empty","kind":"def","line":77,"name":"Computation.empty","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#