<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`head c` is the first step of computation, either `some a` if `c = pure a`\nor `none` if `c = think c'`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.head","kind":"def","line":66,"name":"Computation.head","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L66-L69"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.thinkN\"><span class=\"name\">Computation</span>.<span class=\"name\">thinkN</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation\">Computation</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`thinkN c n` is the computation that delays for `n` ticks and then performs\ncomputation `c`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.html#Computation.thinkN","kind":"def","line":59,"name":"Computation.thinkN","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computation.lean#L59-L63"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Seq/Computa